name: XtReMiX UltiMate Merge
description:
My goal is to make one of the best merges on the web. Of course, to get to the quality of the images that I have uploaded, some adjustments are necessary.

One of the most important things is to use for the full experience (but not necessary):

https://civitai.com/models/45448/full-feature-character-prompts-fantasy with their corresponding Loras/LyCORIS/Textuals inversions mentioned in their section

Another important point is to use good negatives prompts, look at the ones in the images that I have uploaded

And another strong recomendation to use is ADetailer with face_yolov8n:

https://huggingface.co/Bingsu/adetailer

v1.8: I'm working on trying to avoid having to use ADetailer, still necessary for full body pictures, but it have improved a lot.

Also improved the realism and the variety and better details.
